; Coverage test for annotate.cc L302, L313-315, L317-318
; Tests annotated_commodity_t::find_price with fixated price (=) and
; non-fixated price annotations, covering:
;   L302: when = CURRENT_TIME() fallback when no moment specified
;   L313-315: fixated price path returns immediately
;   L317-318: non-fixated price sets target commodity from annotation

P 2024/01/01 EUR $1.10
P 2024/06/01 EUR $1.20

; Fixated price: always uses $1.15 regardless of market price
2024/01/01 Buy Fixed
    Assets:Fixed     10 EUR {=$1.15}
    Assets:Cash

; Non-fixated price: uses market price
2024/01/01 Buy Market
    Assets:Market    10 EUR {$1.05}
    Assets:Cash

test bal -V Assets:Fixed
              $11.50  Assets:Fixed
end test

test bal -V Assets:Market
              $12.00  Assets:Market
end test
